# VHS tape file for the README GIF.
# Install VHS: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
# Then run:    vhs examples/demo.tape
# Output:      examples/demo.gif

Output examples/demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "python examples/demo.py"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 8s
